  "texts": [
    "Overall, Bonito enables practitioners to adapt large language models to tasks on their data without annotations.",
    "Our work relies on the availability of large amounts of unannotated text.",
    "If only a small quantity of unannotated text is present, the target language model, after adaptation, may experience a drop in performance.",
    "While we demonstrate positive improvements on pretrained and instruction-tuned models, our observations are limited to the three task types considered in our experiments.",
    "Bonito poses risks similar to those of any large language model."
  ],
